    <body>
      <pb n="1" facs="../images/26728_1.png"/>
      <div type="letter">
        <opener>
          <dateline>
            <placeName>Burlington</placeName>
            <date when="1852-11-06">Nov. 6 1852</date>
          </dateline>
        </opener>
        <p>
          <persName ref="psn:peter_still">Peter Stills</persName> (a co<del rend="strikethrough"
            >h</del>loured man), has lived in<lb/> my employ for some months past, but<lb/> have
          known him for two years.<lb/>
        </p>

        <p> It affords me much pleasure in being able<lb/> to <choice>
            <orig>reccommend</orig>
            <reg>recommend</reg>
          </choice> him, as an honest sober,<lb/> industrious &amp; capable man, perfectly
          trustworthy<lb/> &amp; ever willing to make himself generally<lb/>
          <choice>
            <orig>usefull</orig>
            <reg>useful</reg>
          </choice> either about the house<lb/> or stable, I part with him reluctantly,<lb/> he
          leaves me, to make an effort to redeem<lb/> his <persName ref="psn:vina_still"
            >wife</persName> &amp; children from slavery<lb/>
        </p>

        <closer>
          <signed><persName ref="psn:elias_boudinot">E. E. Boudinot</persName></signed>
        </closer>
      </div>

      <postscript>
        <ab>
          <add hand="#MB"> The above named Peter Still was in my<lb/> employ ten months, during
            which time he<lb/> fully sustained the character given him by<lb/> M<hi
              rend="superscript">r</hi> Boudinot. It gives me pleasure to add<lb/> my name to this recommmendation. <lb/>
            <persName rendition="#indent3" ref="psn:mary_buckman"> Mary A. Buckman </persName><lb/>
          </add>
        </ab>
      </postscript>

      <postscript>
        <ab>
          <add hand="#CVR"> Judge Boudinot is one of our principal citizens, &amp; I have
            entire<lb/> confidence in his recommendation of Peter Still. <lb/>
            <placeName> Burlington, N.J., </placeName>
            <date when="1852-11-06">Nov. 6/52 </date><!-- floats left -->
            <persName ref="psn:van_rensselaer"> Cortlandt Van Rensselaer </persName>
            <!-- floats right -->
          </add>
        </ab>
      </postscript>

